==English==
===Noun===
# The name for the eighteenth letter of the [[Classical Greek|Classical]] and [[Modern Greek]], the nineteenth letter of [[Old Greek|Old]] and [[Ancient Greek|Ancient]].
# ''(mathematics):'' Used to indicate summation of a set or series, as the symbol &#931;.
# ''(statistics):'' The symbol &#963; is used to indicate one [[standard deviation]] from the [[mean]], particularly in a [[normal distribution]].

